              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "IOCH"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Gridded ionization chamber (GIC) for",
                " alpha-particles detection. Working gas Kr+ 3% ch(4) at",
                "0.6 atm pressure.",
                "Alpha-particle detection efficiency was calculate by",
